sellerCard.description:
Hey there! Are you ready to take your online presence to the next level?

Look no further!

I'm Azhar Mehmood, a qualified and multitalented Graphic designer and WordPress website developer with over 6 years of experience.

I can create any type of graphics, branding, book cover design, book layout design, flyers, posters, websites, blogs, e-commerce stores, and business websites.

Looking forward to working with you and making something amazing together!

description.content:
Hey,

Need a stunning WordPress website that not only looks amazing but also boosts your business? Your search ends here! I treat your business like my own, with care and dedication. Let's turn your vision into a powerful online reality!


I will develop a WordPress website with a responsive web design

  • eCommerce Store
  • Blog / News
  • Video Sharing
  • Fashion 
  • Booking website design
  • Entertainment 
  • Clinic/Medical Lab / Hospital

And many more...


Features:

  • Fully responsive, SEO-optimized, and mobile-friendly Design
  • Manage an unlimited number of categories and products
  • Product shipping options
  • Social media integration
  • SEO friendly Website
  • Autoresponders (Mailchimp etc)
  • Shopping Cart
  • Live Chat
  • Coupon system
  • Product Reviews,Variation

And many more


Why choose me?


  • 100% satisfaction is guaranteed.
  • Over 6 Years of Experience
  • Video guidance for a comprehensive understanding of your website's features.
  • Unlimited Revisions.
  • Created 300+ Sites
  • Complete site setup on hosting and domain (if required).


Check my portfolio : https://www.fiverr.com/users/sialvi931/portfolio


For any kind of questions, just send a message. I'll be happy to assist you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if your requirements does not meet any of my package?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Dont worry, just contact me and we will discuss your requirements and will come up with a customized package or cost.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer unlimited revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. I Will provide you unlimited revisions until your satisfaction.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you solve the issue problems after the order is marked done?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, your satisfactions is my priority my main goal is to have clients that can depend on me as clients are biggest assets in any business. to do that i always walk an extra mile .

questionsAndAnswers.question: I am new to this whole thing what should i do?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Basic block of website is domain name and hosting package if you don't know any good hosting companies feel free to contact me,i will recommend you according to your requirements Thanks:)

questionsAndAnswers.question: I don't know how to manage my website will you help me with that?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I always give a walkthrough to my clients from the Website once everything is done so they can take care of basic content editing image changing managing on their own and also answer any kind of questions, to make major customization/additions or changes you can open a small job with me. :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you redesign my existing wordpress website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can Redesign your existing website.
